english.segment1: I don't know what to say. No words could ever be enough. I stand up because you hold me here. Because you brought me here tonight
english.segment2: Without you we all fall down. Without you we all fall
english.segment3: You make life worth living. You make me want to start giving. More and more away to you. It's not mine anyway
english.segment4: I could not ever try so hard. I could buy a place in your heart. But here I am. My name written on your hands. Because you paid the debt I owe
